text: Elhadji Tacko Sereigne Diop Fall (born 10 December 1995) is a Senegalese professional basketball player. He plays for Piratas de Quebradillas. He was born in Dakar, Senegal. Mamadou N'Diaye wanted Fall to attend his basketball academy. He moved to the United States when he was 16 years old. He played basketball in Houston, Texas.
